%% State — Chat Session
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> open: Customer gửi message đầu tiên<br/>(sessionId mới)

  open --> waiting_bot: POST /api/chat/send
  waiting_bot --> open: AI/rule-based trả lời<br/>→ ChatMessage(assistant)

  open --> escalated: Admin tham gia<br/>(role=admin)
  escalated --> open: Admin xong / im lặng > N phút

  open --> archived: Không hoạt động > 24h
  escalated --> archived: Không hoạt động > 24h

  archived --> open: Customer/Admin gửi tiếp
  archived --> closed: Admin xóa session<br/>(DELETE /chat/sessions/:id)

  closed --> [*]

  note right of waiting_bot
    Provider chọn theo env:
    GEMINI_API_KEY > ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
    → fallback rule-based
  end note
